text: Verrall Newman (21 January 1897 - 7 October 1987) was a British diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1897 births Category:1987 deaths Category:British female divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hampstead
